#Contribution Guidelines

Please ensure your pull request meet to the following guidelines:

- Search previous suggestions before making a new one, as yours may be a duplicate.
- **Make an individual pull request for each suggestion: article, spreadshit or tool.**
- Use the following format: `[PACKAGE](LINK) - DESCRIPTION.`
- Try to make your pull request and title as descriptive as possible.
- New categories, or improvements to the existing categorization are welcome.
- End all descriptions with a full stop/period.
- Check your spelling and grammar.
- Make sure that your suggestion is positioned as the last item category.
- Make sure your text editor is set to remove trailing whitespace.


## Link Format
Please, use the folowing format for the links:
* ``[Title of the Article](link) by Author``
* ``[Name on the tool](link) by Author``
  
Your contributions are always welcome!  Thank you for your suggestions! :smiley:
